Title: Zootopia Official Sloth Trailer (2016) - Disney Animated Movie HD
Comment:
I don't mind the sloth joke.  I really don't.  We get it:  The DMV takes forever.  Hah.  
But this is a fine example of a joke that should have been just a passing gag.  Stretching it out as long as this is just lazy filler.  And my biggest peeve?  Stating the obvious.  I absolutely hate it when characters feel the need to state the obvious.  We can see they are sloths.  We can see it's night-time.  Movie-goers are not retarded, seriously.
Well, okay, I might be wrong on that last part, given the demographic this movie panders to.... but seriously, even Furries can get jokes with minimal hand-holding.  Not that you'd want to hold their hands after where they've been.
